00:15:42.620 --> 00:15:44.270
But if you're in
the world of finance

00:15:44.270 --> 00:15:47.450
or you're in the world of inter
mediating risk and holding

00:15:47.450 --> 00:15:47.960
risks--

00:15:47.960 --> 00:15:51.060
so volatility is a form of risk.

00:15:51.060 --> 00:15:53.030
So volatility was
always our friend.

00:15:53.030 --> 00:15:54.980
It was also our
friend, because often

00:15:54.980 --> 00:15:57.380
if it was really
volatile, sometimes some

00:15:57.380 --> 00:16:01.070
of our competitors would not
manage that risk as well.

00:16:01.070 --> 00:16:02.780
And they would
lose market share,

00:16:02.780 --> 00:16:04.540
