laws-- money transmission

00:41:55.150 --> 00:41:58.930
laws are the laws that were
just mentioned by Daniel,

00:41:58.930 --> 00:42:00.520
the anti-money laundering.

00:42:00.520 --> 00:42:04.090
CTF is counter-terrorism
finance.

00:42:04.090 --> 00:42:08.170
