00:42:11.980 --> 00:42:16.600
It first is one of the things in
the US Department of Treasury--

00:42:16.600 --> 00:42:18.640
but again, to
internationalize it--

00:42:18.640 --> 00:42:21.970
other departments of treasury
and so forth around the globe

00:42:21.970 --> 00:42:27.330
define when do you come
under the similar laws.

00:42:27.330 --> 00:42:30.760
When are you just a
user of this property,

00:42:30.760 --> 00:42:32.470
because it's not a currency?

00:42:32.470 --> 00:42:35.140
But to confuse matters, the
US Department of treasury

00:42:35.140 --> 00:42:39.670
