property for tax law.

00:42:42.580 --> 00:42:44.500
This is two parts of
the same department.

00:42:44.500 --> 00:42:46.600
The US Department of
treasury said it's property

00:42:46.600 --> 00:42:47.800
not currency.

00:42:47.800 --> 00:42:51.410
Another part of the US Treasury
said it's virtual currency.

00:42:51.410 --> 00:42:54.010
And the reason they had to
say it was virtual currency

00:42:54.010 --> 00:42:58.780
is they wanted it to come under
this law, the Bank Secrecy Act,

00:42:58.780 --> 00:43:01.950
without going probably to
Congress to have it be amended.

