01:15:47.550 --> 01:15:53.730
a broader range of
decision making, but also

01:15:53.730 --> 01:15:58.830
always remember they live in
a world of asymmetric risk.

01:15:58.830 --> 01:16:01.830
There's not much
upside to saying yes

01:16:01.830 --> 01:16:06.180
to something new, and funky,
and hard, and difficult,

01:16:06.180 --> 01:16:09.450
but they could be getting
a host of downside risk

01:16:09.450 --> 01:16:11.820
if it blows up on their watch.

01:16:11.820 --> 01:16:14.010
So there's asymmetric risk.

01:16:14.010 --> 01:16:17.580
And Bitcoin and
